// CVD Analysis
"cvd.analysis.intro" = "Would you like to see what someone who has CVD sees? Ask them to complete the next few screens.

You will be shown a series of colours like the one below.";

"cvd.analysis.explanation" = "People with normal colour vision see a gradient of colours, but people with CVD find it harder to see the gradient and may even see a solid rectangle, depending on the severity.";

"cvd.analysis.instruction.1" = "Move the slider until you see a solid rectangle";
